#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:18
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The thumbnail kioslave is used by &kde; for network transparent and "
#| "persistent generation of thumbnails."
msgid ""
"The thumbnail KIO worker is used by &kde; for network transparent and "
"persistent generation of thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"КДЕ користи У/И захват сличица за мрежно прозирно и трајно стварање сличица."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The thumbnail kioslave uses plugins to generate the actual thumbnails. "
#| "You can enable viewing of these thumbnails from the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preview</guisubmenu></"
#| "menuchoice> submenu, available in &dolphin; or in &konqueror; in file "
#| "manager mode."
msgid ""
"The thumbnail KIO worker uses plugins to generate the actual thumbnails. You "
"can enable viewing of these thumbnails from the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preview</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu, available in "
"&dolphin; or in &konqueror; in file manager mode."
msgstr ""
"У/И захвата сличица користи прикључке за непосредно стварање сличица. У "
"<application>Делфину</application> и у <application>К‑освајачу</application> "
"у режиму менаџера фајлова, приказ сличица можете укључити кроз подмени "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Приказ</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Преглед</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:27
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The thumbnail kioslave is not directly useful to a user, but if you are a "
#| "developer, you can use it within your own applications to create file "
#| "previews."
msgid ""
"The thumbnail KIO worker is not directly useful to a user, but if you are a "
"developer, you can use it within your own applications to create file "
"previews."
msgstr ""
"У/И захват сличица није од непосредне важности корисницима, али ако сте "
"програмер, можете га користити у својим програмима за стварање прегледа "
"фајлова."

